        "active": true,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Quick Start Guide",
        "text": "<h2>Quick Start Guide</h2><p>[image]</p><p>Ready to begin? To get started with your first treatment, you'll need the following:</p><ul><li>Neck & Décolletage LED System</li><li>Controller with double USB-C ports (provided)</li><li>Adjustable straps (provided)</li></ul>"
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_image_block_ptjFFA": {
      "type": "n_guide-content-image-block",
