      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content-image-block.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Charging Your Device",
        "text": "<h2>Charging Your Device</h2><p>[image]</p><p>To charge your system, insert the USB-C cable into the bottom of the controller (look for the ⚡ symbol).</p><p>Connect the other end to a USB-C power source.</p><p>While charging, the indicator will flash white. </p><p>When the battery is fully charged, the indicator will be solid white.</p><p>Tips to maximize battery life:</p><ul><li>Avoid leaving your system charging for long periods of time.</li><li>Avoid letting the battery completely run out.</li><li>Do not use your system while it's connected to the charger.</li></ul>"
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_j3tkDV": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Care & Maintenance",
        "text": "<h2>Care & Maintenance</h2><p>Wipe the system down after each treatment. </p><p>Spray with our <a href=\"#\" title=\"#\">Dermal mist</a> to sanitize and keep the system clean for your next use.</p><p>When not in use, store your system in the provided storage pouch. Store it in a cool, moisture-free environment.</p>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_gkdiDb": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Troubleshooting & Adjustments",
        "text": "<h2>Troubleshooting & Adjustments</h2><p>Having trouble? Don't worry, most issues are quick to solve.</p><h6>System is not turning on</h6><ul><li>Make sure the system is fully charged.</li><li>Ensure the USB-C cable is plugged into the correct port on the controller (look for the port marked with the lightning bolt battery symbol).</li><li>Check that the USB-C charging cable is fully inserted when charging.</li><li>Press and hold the ON/OFF button for a full second to activate the product.</li><li>Still nothing? Try a different outlet or charging cable to rule out charging issues.</li></ul><p>[hr]</p><h6>System is turning off too early</h6><p>The battery level may be too low — charge the product fully and try again.</p><p>[hr]</p><h6>Something else?</h6><p>DO NOT attempt to investigate or modify the product. It contains no serviceable parts.</p><p>If the issue persists, please contact Qure Support at <a href=\"mailto:support@qureskincare.com\" title=\"mailto:support@qureskincare.com\">support@qureskincare.com</a> for further assistance.</p>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_faq_XGzmpC": {
      "type": "n_guide-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_item_Ypebcp": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "When will I see results?",
            "text": "<p>Some people notice a glow after just one use, but visible improvements usually happen after a few weeks of consistent use.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_kJGA6W": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How often should I use the Neck & Décolletage LED System?",
            "text": "<p>We recommend using it once per day for a minimum of 4 weeks. After that, continue based on your personal care routine.</p><p>Do not use this system more than 7 times per week.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_D6GhrE": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it everyday?",
            "text": "<p>Yes, it’s safe for daily use. Just stick to one treatment per day.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_bTrpib": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it with my other skincare products?",
            "text": "<p>Yes, but use the mask first on clean, dry skin. You can apply your serums and moisturizers afterward.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_YTxURq": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I clean the mask?",
            "text": "<p>Use a soft, damp cloth to wipe the surface. Don’t use harsh cleaners or submerge it in water.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_KHaJDB": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long does it take to charge?",
            "text": "<p>The Neck & Décolletage fully charges in 4 hours.</p>"
          }
        },
